TITLE: Creating iOS Widget with Directus Data Integration using JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: A complete script for creating an iOS widget using Scriptable that fetches and displays sensor data from Directus. The code handles authentication with a static token, data fetching, processing of sensor values, and widget display formatting. The widget shows different layouts based on the device state and updates periodically as controlled by iOS.
SOURCE: https://github.com/directus/docs/blob/main/content/tutorials/2.projects/use-directus-as-a-baby-health-tracker-with-owlet-and-ops-genie.md#2025-04-09_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: javascript
