TITLE: Implementing Up and Down Migration Functions in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates the structure of a migration file in Directus, exporting async 'up' and 'down' functions that use Knex to create and drop a table respectively.
SOURCE: https://github.com/directus/docs/blob/main/content/configuration/migrations.md#2025-04-09_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
