TITLE: Creating a StatefulSet for MariaDB in a Directus Setup
DESCRIPTION: Defines a StatefulSet for a MariaDB database to be used with Directus. StatefulSets are ideal for stateful applications like databases that require stable network identifiers and persistent storage for each pod.
