TITLE: PM2 Environment Variables Configuration Table
DESCRIPTION: Table of PM2 environment variables used to configure process management for Directus instances. Includes variables for controlling instance count, execution mode, memory limits, uptime monitoring, timeout settings, restart behavior, and log file paths.
