TITLE: Customizing Directus Docker Image for SSO Proxy Support
DESCRIPTION: This Dockerfile extends the Directus image to install global-agent and apply the patch for enabling proxy support in SSO configurations. It includes steps for installing dependencies and applying the patch file.
SOURCE: https://github.com/directus/docs/blob/main/content/guides/3.auth/7.sso/1.index.md#2025-04-09_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: dockerfile
CODE:
```
FROM directus/directus:11.1.1

USER root
RUN corepack enable
USER node

RUN pnpm install global-agent@3

COPY ecosystem-global-agent.patch .

USER root
RUN <<EOF
	apk add --no-cache patch
	patch -p1 < ecosystem-global-agent.patch || exit 1
	rm ecosystem-global-agent.patch
	apk del patch
EOF
USER node
```

